{"tid":1955352,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"4月2日西鐵線早上荃灣西站有人摸野,好嘔","createTime":"2020-04-02T11:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T13:43:20.000Z","uid":269202,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d26713a4481b42e4ddc6eebe4f00dd7f61674a9","tid":1955352,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:59:24.000Z","msg":"話說係4月2號早上約8:45，列車駛至荃灣西，發現車內一名黄色衣著男人，他左手維持圖中手勢反手，並故意挑動、觸碰一個年輕人下體。雖然年輕人都不是第一次遇到怪叔叔，當時也希望對方只是不小心。但事後會不斷回想片段，清楚知道是自己騙自己，總覺得應該行駛公民拘捕權。<br />\n年輕人移開手上手機，清見到下方有隻手像圖中手勢。<br />\n現在過了數小時仍不斷回想片段，有不好感受，這是被侵犯者的怪感覺？年輕人不接受男人。<br />\n大家小心搭車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfWJXPn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfWJXPn.png&h=5ebac2a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9fc6e2b78738bdf1655c835c056a9a7991139e7","tid":1955352,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"唔打柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858289ba2e95b7354be7f9a226612134fa168a91","tid":1955352,"uid":318028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9fc6e2b78738bdf1655c835c056a9a7991139e7","tid":1955352,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"唔打柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"應該彈返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fac7081d965d98ab3b4ea4a3821c47ca31d89c9","tid":1955352,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fc6e2b78738bdf1655c835c056a9a7991139e7","tid":1955352,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"唔打柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"唔係咁易架葉師傅，我以前試過俾人從後聞我<br />\n唔敢郁<br />\n<br />\n今次敢退開已經有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hk